@support_neorev_progress

We attempt to convince the party to support the creation of a European Union. Advocates of the plan argue that this plan will distribute the economic burden more equitably and bring long-term benefits. Opponents in other factions criticize the plan for being impractical and a deviation from Marxist principles.

We have not yet adopted the plan. More work needs to be done.

