@true_support

Only by through worker solidarity can we protect each other against capitalist depredations. Labor is somewhat critical of our efforts. The German workers are starving; are we going to #abandon them while we chase an utopian dream? On the other hand, traditionalist centrists lambast their colleagues for sowing discord under the guise of promoting unity.

